name: UnSafe Exam Browser v3.7.1
body:
[![Latest Release Downloads](https://img.shields.io/github/downloads/wxnnvs/seb-win-bypass/v3.7.1/total.svg)]()

Bypass Safe Exam Browser limitations >:)
(Now updated to v3.7.1)

#### **Features**
- [x] Open any url
- [x] Quit without password
- [ ] Run programs

#### **How to use?**
1. Install [Safe Exam Browser 3.7.1](https://github.com/SafeExamBrowser/seb-win-refactoring/releases/download/v3.7.1/SEB_3.7.1.704_SetupBundle.exe)
2. Download `SafeExamBrowser.Browser.dll`
3. Navigate to `C:\Program Files\SafeExamBrowser\Application`
4. Copy the downloaded file to this folder
5. Press `Replace`
6. Start an exam
7. Press `F9` on your keyboard
8. Enjoy!
